uiEntry.title: traits_title
uiEntry.tooltip: Traits are earned and created by the character's actions and experience over the game.||They can provide additional bonuses on the campaign and battle map and give a strategic use to specific characters.||Some may be economically minded and suited to running a city, whereas others are more at home on the battlefield.||Move your cursor over the traits to see their effects.||Not all traits are desirable, some traits are effectively penalties!||If this happens some damage control may be in order - move the character into a position where they can play to their strengths rather than fall prey to their weaknesses!||Move the cursor over the traits to see their effects.
